    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Chunk and Embed\n\n**Purpose:** Processes text documents by chunking them into manageable segments and generating embeddings for vector search.\n\n**Input:** Expects `text_content`, `document_id`, and optional `collection_name` from calling workflow.\n\n**Process:**\n1. Splits text into ~2000 character chunks with 200 character overlap\n2. Processes each chunk individually through the loop\n3. Generates embeddings via KB__GenerateEmbedding workflow\n4. Stores chunk text + embedding in Supabase `embeddings_metadata` table\n\n**Output:** Returns `chunk_count` for tracking.\n\n**Used by:** KB workflows that need to index documents for semantic search.",
        "height": 672,
        "width": 1312,
        "color": 4
      },
